msgid "After the catalogue feed finishes, also fetch each book's technical sheet (dimensions, weight, page count, binding, NCM) -- one by-ISBN call per book, queued as a follow-up job since it is far slower than the feed. Import by ISBN already carries the technical sheet, so this only applies to the publisher (catalogue) import."
